50|$|A small {{stretch of}} the Volga River flows through eastern <b>Kalmykia.</b> Other major rivers include the Yegorlyk, the Kuma, and the Manych. Lake Manych-Gudilo is the largest lake; other lakes of {{significance}} include Lakes Sarpa and Tsagan-Khak. In all, however, <b>Kalmykia</b> possesses few lakes.|$|E
